steps.instruction:
From Publix Aprons and can be found [here](https://ww4.publix.com/recipes-planning/aprons-simple-meals/mushroom-swiss-burgers-with-chopped-cauliflower-salad)  
Pairs well with [Mushroom Swiss Burgers](http://67.9.187.149/view/recipe/263)

### Prep
- Coarsely chop the cashews
- Thaw out the green peas
- Cut cauliflower into 1/2-inch pieces
- Chop basil
- Combine yogurt and dressing in salad bowl.

### Steps
1. dd remaining ingredients to dressing; toss to coat
2. Let stand 10 minutes for flavors to blend. Serve.
